page_title: Quickstart: Generate images with Azure OpenAI Service using PowerShell
page_description: Learn how to generate images with Azure OpenAI Service by using PowerShell and the endpoint and access keys for your Azure OpenAI resource.
chunk_content: Clean up resourcesIf you want to clean up and remove an Azure OpenAI resource, you can delete the resource or resource group. Deleting the resource group also deletes any other resources associated with it.- Azure portal- Azure PowerShell
